      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new streetwear line and i really wanna make sure i get the vibe right. i want it to feel authentic to actual urban culture so it doesn't come off as just some shallow appropriation or something. can you describe what the 'authentic' urban aesthetic is like right now? like, what are the key elements that define it?",
